SingleEvent.create(:id => 2137, :name => "Chillout", :description => "Teil der [Interactive Cologne](http://www.nerdhub.de/events/256-interactive-cologne/dates/1743)\r\n\r\n**Talks:**\r\n\r\n- Jan Kus\r\n- if you think you have something to say just ping us on [twitter](http://twitter.com/interactive_cgn) or write an [email](jan@railslove.com).\r\n\r\nThis event's place will be announced ASAP. The entrance is free and for more information visit: [http://devhousefriday.org/networks/events/show_event.78620](http://devhousefriday.org/networks/events/show_event.78620)", :event_id => 9, :occurrence => Fri, 21 Jun 2013 19:00:00 CEST +02:00, :url => "http://interactive-cologne.com/devhousefriday.html", :duration => 120, :full_day => false, :based_on_rule => false, :category_id => 3, :use_venue_info_of_event => true)
