SingleEvent.create(:id => 1283, :description => "It's 2013, and it is time for evoke again. but this time, we are doing some things different. \r\nNew and innovative compos in addition to the classics, more entertainment for you to enjoy, all wrapped up with what we know how to do best: A Party with a heart.\r\n\r\n**NEW COMPETITIONS**\r\n\r\n**INTERACTIVE**\r\n- this is a new competition, in which we want you to explore new types artforms. any application that involves human interaction to generate visual and or audio feedback to the audience is allowed.\r\n\r\nsince this is a new compo and we try to engage new platform we are open to any kind of submission\r\n\r\n**GET CREATIVE AND EXPERIMENTAL! WE EMBRACE ANY KIND OF INPUT**\r\n\r\n- keyboard, mouse, gamepad\r\n- wii controler\r\n- kinect\r\n- trackpad\r\n- EXAMPLES OF INTERACTIVE APPLICATIONS:\r\n- games\r\n- interactive demos\r\n- narrative story-telling\r\n- music disks\r\n- experimental visualization of user input\r\n\r\n**RULES**\r\n\r\n- every platform is allowed\r\n- must not been released before\r\n- we endorse you to present it live in the competition\r\n- a microphone will be provided for additional commenting\r\n- maximum running time: 5 minutes\r\n- please contact us if:\r\n- need or bring special hardware other than our compo pc\r\n- especially if you provide a video signal other than dvi or composite\r\n- we will show the usual output and also the interaction on a second display\r\n- executable will be released\r\n\r\n\r\n**PIXEL GRAPHICS**\r\n\r\nyou have to create an image which uses a limited palette. The Palette will be provided by us in the near future.\r\n\r\n\r\n- this compo is open to contributions of people who are not present at the party\r\n- we will provide a website where you can upload your final entry\r\n- you can choose the resolution, 16:9 aspect ratio is recommended\r\n- final image must not be released before\r\n- GIF Animation is allowed\r\n- max. showtime per entry is 30 seconds\r\n- there will be a preselection, e.g. badly converted content will be disqualified\r\n\r\n", :event_id => 21, :occurrence => Fri, 16 Aug 2013 10:00:00 CEST +02:00, :full_day => true, :based_on_rule => false, :category_id => 3, :picture_id => 225, :use_venue_info_of_event => true)
